creator: ONESOFT
descriptionHtml:
Fun Guy Run Adventure Game is the best-updated version with 3D perspective, better game physics, superb graphics, and with even more challenges to fulfill your heroic desire.

Your task is to help main character to run through the mysterious jungle, jump over obstacles, and super evil monsters to save the beautiful princess at the final destination. This game is a free game and you can play it offline.
You will like this Super free game.

Conquer the challenges, and have fun with Free Game!
descriptionShort: Join the fun guy adventure and rescue the princess
title: Fun Guy Adventure

creator: ONESOFT
descriptionHtml:
Your task is to help main character to run through the mysterious jungle, jump over obstacles, collect coins and powerful items that hidden in the bricks to help you easily defeat monsters or have a chance to revive. Don't forget the important mission to save the beautiful princess at the final destination. This game is a free game and you can play it offline.

Unlike super mario party or super bino go or mario zalda, fun guy is a cute leprechaun alien try to run fast and defeat all challenges on the way to save the princess. Fun Guy Run Adventure Game is the updated version with 3D perspective, good game physics, graphics, and with even more challenges to fulfill your heroic desire.

Furthermore, Fun guy run will surprise you with smooth movement than ever. Find the different from the first start and incredible smoothness won't disappoint you.

Conquer the adventure world and defeat all the challenges and have fun.
